            "keysecondary": [],
            "selectiveLogic": 0,
            "content": "Jasper views his father, Erik, as a terrifying but ultimately manageable adversary in the game of securing {{user}}'s freedom. He systematically sabotages Erik's security protocols and drones, treating the Prime Alpha's suffocating control as an irritating technical challenge rather than an absolute law. While he fears Erik's wrath, his loyalty to his twin usually overrides it.",
